The paper deals with the problem of Private Information Retrieval (PIR), which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of side information also brings in elements of data structures (cs.DS) and coding theory (cs.CC). Finally, the paper deals with a database of messages, which is a topic in databases (cs.DB).
